      查看完整的更新日志。（中文）
    </p>

    <br>
    <hr>
    <br>

    <p>
      See the whole changelog at the
      <a href="https://github.com/DragonKnightOfBreeze/Idea-Plugins/blob/master/stellaris-modding-support/README.md">README</a> and
